1
00:00:13,720 --> 00:00:14,360
Draw your sword.

2
00:01:05,280 --> 00:01:06,520
This is not your martial skill.

3
00:01:07,120 --> 00:01:08,800
If it's not mine, could it be yours?

4
00:01:09,480 --> 00:01:12,359
How could you improve
so much in just a few days?

5
00:01:12,359 --> 00:01:15,079
Want to know?
Hand over the seal, and I'll tell you.

6
00:01:48,040 --> 00:01:50,599
Muqing, how did you become so powerful?

7
00:01:52,799 --> 00:01:57,159
It's because he has become weaker.
He might be injured.

8
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:12,879
I felt especially uneasy at night.

9
00:02:13,439 --> 00:02:16,160
I only found out you went to report
back to Prince Qi after asking them.

10
00:02:16,800 --> 00:02:18,880
I couldn't help but run out to find you.

11
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:21,879
Who knew you would encounter Men Sandao?

12
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:23,879
I'm fine.

13
00:02:34,439 --> 00:02:37,680
You were slow
because you were just injured.

14
00:02:40,080 --> 00:02:42,840
Otherwise, how could he
possibly be your match?

15
00:02:44,199 --> 00:02:48,800
No, I wanted to end the fight soon,

16
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:50,120
so I wasn't slow at all.

17
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:54,920
But he remembered every move
of my sword technique.

18
00:02:54,920 --> 00:02:56,520
Every time, he could get the upper hand.

19
00:03:00,039 --> 00:03:01,560
He wasn't that skilled before.

20
00:03:06,680 --> 00:03:07,600
His knife.

21
00:03:10,840 --> 00:03:15,719
That's right. He used a knife
but sword techniques.

22
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:20,360
The Sanyin Sword.

23
00:03:27,759 --> 00:03:31,800
Men Sandao has made
such progress in such a short time.

24
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:35,280
He must have received
the Bodhi heritage at the Futu Temple.

25
00:03:38,759 --> 00:03:42,439
The Sanyin Sword is truly formidable.

26
00:03:53,080 --> 00:03:55,639
The Shaolin skills are so formidable.

27
00:03:58,320 --> 00:04:00,560
I must find the Altar Treasure

28
00:04:01,200 --> 00:04:03,440
to read through
all the techniques contained within.

29
00:04:13,668 --> 00:04:17,696
(I'm Zhuo Bufan,
always in pursuit and extraordinary.)

30
00:04:18,400 --> 00:04:22,048
(Only those who can wander everywhere
are worthy of this name.)

31
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:26,280
(My life is a gamble with fate, a wager
on life and death, a bet on the future.)

32
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:28,800
(Life is unfair,
and I fell on an evil time.)

33
00:04:29,480 --> 00:04:32,440
(I do whatever I can to change my fate.)

34
00:04:32,440 --> 00:04:36,000
(Everything is impermanent and fickle.)

35
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:38,400
(I will decide my own life and death.)

36
00:04:39,320 --> 00:04:42,000
(I bet on a promising future
and a great undertaking.)

37
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:44,080
(I want to protect the last hope.)

38
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:48,320
(But I lost the bet on her.)

39
00:04:48,320 --> 00:04:49,360
(10 taels)

40
00:04:49,360 --> 00:04:53,000
(I thought we couldn't meet
the right one too late.)

41
00:04:53,760 --> 00:04:58,400
(But actually,
meeting too early also will not do.)

42
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:01,800
(I always remember
the first time I met her.)

43
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:05,184
(She stood beside the flowers, smiling.)

44
00:05:05,840 --> 00:05:08,768
(Later on, even though she
has been by my side,)

45
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:11,640
(she can't be for a lifetime.)

46
00:05:11,640 --> 00:05:14,040
(I never know her answer.)

47
00:05:14,040 --> 00:05:17,280
(When I was young,
I always pursued that answer.)

48
00:05:17,280 --> 00:05:19,680
(But after a long time,)

49
00:05:19,680 --> 00:05:22,680
(I only wish that no fights)

50
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:25,408
(and lovers get together.)

51
00:05:28,772 --> 00:05:33,408
=Heroes=

52
00:05:34,500 --> 00:05:36,384
=Episode 24=

53
00:05:47,080 --> 00:05:51,400
Just a regular merchant.
He often comes by to peddle some goods.

54
00:05:51,400 --> 00:05:55,040
The prices are quite high,
but the goods are also quite good.

55
00:05:56,080 --> 00:05:57,840
Why would you ask about this?

56
00:05:57,840 --> 00:06:02,280
He gave me gifts.
Shouldn't I at least know who he is?

57
00:06:03,360 --> 00:06:07,519
His name is Lin Haohan,
but he calls himself Lucky.

58
00:06:08,839 --> 00:06:09,600
Lucky.

59
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:12,560
In English, it means good luck.

60
00:06:14,240 --> 00:06:17,000
He's quite lucky.

61
00:06:17,760 --> 00:06:20,880
Are you sure he's just
an ordinary merchant?

62
00:06:24,560 --> 00:06:26,400
He's just an ordinary merchant.

63
00:06:27,000 --> 00:06:31,000
He goes around buying and selling goods.

64
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:33,040
He has sold quite a few things
to the princess.

65
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:34,720
He must have made quite a bit of money.

66
00:06:34,720 --> 00:06:37,640
Lin Haohan
has recently set up a big shop.

67
00:06:37,640 --> 00:06:39,000
It's going to be open soon.

68
00:06:39,000 --> 00:06:41,199
I hear he has even invited the princess.

69
00:06:42,400 --> 00:06:43,520
Then it must be a coincidence?

70
00:06:44,200 --> 00:06:45,400
Yes, a coincidence.

71
00:06:45,400 --> 00:06:49,200
His gift isn't worth much in itself.

72
00:06:49,200 --> 00:06:52,880
The material and workmanship
are both mediocre. It isn't top-notch.

73
00:06:52,880 --> 00:06:54,920
But it's a good choice for a gift.

74
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:58,319
For a businessman,
it makes sense to give you

75
00:06:58,319 --> 00:07:03,160
that not-too-expensive-or-cheap thing.

76
00:07:03,160 --> 00:07:06,840
Good.

77
00:07:06,840 --> 00:07:12,480
Anyway, he's unintentionally rendered
a great help.

78
00:07:36,160 --> 00:07:37,399
You slept on the floor yesterday.

79
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:40,920
I'll sleep on the floor today.
You sleep on the bed.

80
00:07:42,280 --> 00:07:44,399
It's alright. I'm a man.
I can sleep on the floor.

81
00:07:50,880 --> 00:07:52,400
I'll accompany you
and sleep on the floor.

82
00:07:52,400 --> 00:07:53,240
No.

83
00:07:54,880 --> 00:07:56,040
Or you sleep on the bed with me.

84
00:07:56,040 --> 00:07:56,879
That's even worse.

85
00:08:02,760 --> 00:08:04,800
Is sleeping with me a terrible thing?

86
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:09,439
I don't mind it.
You're a man. Why do you even care?

87
00:08:13,320 --> 00:08:15,120
I am already yours.

88
00:08:16,560 --> 00:08:20,360
Sorry for disrespecting you last time.

89
00:08:20,360 --> 00:08:22,519
As a highly educated man,

90
00:08:22,519 --> 00:08:24,319
how could I do such a disgraceful thing?

91
00:08:40,840 --> 00:08:43,760
I've already thought it through.
Once I close the case, I will

92
00:08:48,680 --> 00:08:51,000
propose to you.

93
00:08:54,720 --> 00:08:56,440
My master has gone.

94
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:59,639
We are the same,
without family in the world.

95
00:09:01,639 --> 00:09:03,000
But I can become your family.

96
00:09:04,120 --> 00:09:06,200
I will absolutely never let you
suffer any grievances again.

97
00:09:24,240 --> 00:09:27,680
I believe you.
I'll wait for you to marry me.

98
00:09:28,240 --> 00:09:33,320
I will marry no one but you.

99
00:09:42,039 --> 00:09:43,679
Go to bed.
I'm going out for some fresh air.

100
00:09:45,120 --> 00:09:47,919
Come back early. I'm afraid of the dark.

101
00:09:47,919 --> 00:09:48,840
I'll be back in a moment.

102
00:09:58,240 --> 00:09:58,944
(Changde Inn)

103
00:10:11,440 --> 00:10:16,200
Stop. Back up.

104
00:10:19,240 --> 00:10:20,560
Jialuo.

105
00:10:20,560 --> 00:10:21,440
Haohan.

106
00:10:21,440 --> 00:10:23,159
What are the odds?

107
00:10:24,720 --> 00:10:27,240
I've been dozing off all the way.

108
00:10:27,240 --> 00:10:29,880
And with just a glance, I saw you.

109
00:10:29,880 --> 00:10:32,120
My shop just happens to open tomorrow.

110
00:10:32,120 --> 00:10:35,080
I've been wanting to invite you,
but I just couldn't find you.

111
00:10:35,080 --> 00:10:36,679
And now we've bumped
into each other like this.

112
00:10:37,600 --> 00:10:38,440
This is the invitation.

113
00:10:39,040 --> 00:10:39,920
(Beijing Qianmen Street)
This is the address.

114
00:10:39,920 --> 00:10:42,879
Jialuo, your presence would be an honor.

115
00:10:42,879 --> 00:10:44,679
Our good buddy,
Men Sandao, will be there too.

116
00:10:45,320 --> 00:10:46,919
It's been a long time
since we saw each other.

117
00:10:47,639 --> 00:10:49,400
Okay. Congratulations.

118
00:10:49,400 --> 00:10:50,120
Thank you.

119
00:10:50,120 --> 00:10:50,759
Congratulations.

120
00:10:50,759 --> 00:10:51,440
Thank you.

121
00:10:51,440 --> 00:10:52,039
Congratulations.

122
00:10:52,039 --> 00:10:53,759
Thank you. You talk so much.

123
00:10:55,240 --> 00:10:56,200
This is...?

124
00:10:56,200 --> 00:11:01,240
(10-tael banknote)
Can you please give this to me tomorrow?

125
00:11:01,240 --> 00:11:02,559
Do me a favor.

126
00:11:02,559 --> 00:11:06,720
In return, this is
my thank-you gift. Keep it well.

127
00:11:09,639 --> 00:11:11,879
It was unexpected,
so I didn't bring a gift.

128
00:11:11,879 --> 00:11:14,679
I mean, the gift for you.

129
00:11:14,679 --> 00:11:15,480
No need.

130
00:11:15,480 --> 00:11:16,039
No.

131
00:11:16,039 --> 00:11:19,240
It's your shop's opening.
I should give you a gift. Take it back.

132
00:11:19,240 --> 00:11:23,720
Exactly. The gift for you to give me.

133
00:11:23,720 --> 00:11:26,679
But it's okay.
We're good buddies. Forget that.

134
00:11:26,679 --> 00:11:29,120
It's the thought that counts.
The Qianmen Street.

135
00:11:32,120 --> 00:11:34,279
There's one more thing, Jialuo.

136
00:11:34,919 --> 00:11:39,120
Could you please come
in your Beiyang Army uniform tomorrow?

137
00:11:39,120 --> 00:11:43,000
That way, others will see
that I have connections in the military.

138
00:11:43,639 --> 00:11:46,640
Remember. The Qianmen Street
and the military uniform.

139
00:11:46,640 --> 00:11:48,480
The Qianmen... Military...

140
00:11:48,480 --> 00:11:50,360
The Qianmen Street
and the military uniform. I got it.

141
00:11:50,879 --> 00:11:53,320
Right. Jialuo, remember.

142
00:11:53,320 --> 00:11:55,520
Let's go. Please don't forget.

143
00:11:55,520 --> 00:11:57,480
Jialuo, please don't forget.

144
