♪You and I were inseparable in the past♪

473
00:37:50,163 --> 00:37:53,587
♪I once thought♪

474
00:37:54,611 --> 00:37:58,067
♪We would be together forever
in this life♪

475
00:37:58,291 --> 00:38:05,043
♪Yet we parted ways♪

476
