♪I want to be by your side♪

477
00:38:09,747 --> 00:38:13,235
♪Even if people give me stares♪

478
00:38:13,683 --> 00:38:16,147
♪I am not willing♪

479
00:38:16,307 --> 00:38:20,691
♪To meet you only in dreams♪

480
00:38:21,235 --> 00:38:24,563
♪I want to snuggle with you♪

481
00:38:25,043 --> 00:38:28,403
♪Even if people will judge♪

482
00:38:28,915 --> 00:38:31,283
♪Only wish in the next life♪

483
00:38:31,731 --> 00:38:35,955
♪We can be a happy couple♪

484
