♪I want to be by your side♪

485
00:38:42,003 --> 00:38:45,555
♪Even if people give me stares♪

486
00:38:46,035 --> 00:38:48,691
♪I am not willing♪

487
00:38:48,915 --> 00:38:53,299
♪To meet you only in dreams♪

488
00:38:53,587 --> 00:38:56,915
♪I want to snuggle with you♪

